id: pm-vnjh
title: Reusable external npm package ecosystem smoke harness
description: "Follow-up from pm-lwtx ecosystem lane: external audit manually discovered npm packages with npm search 'pm-cli pm-package' and verified isolated install + package doctor + runtime availability for 15 current packages. Duplicate check: pm search external npm package smoke harness discover pm-cli pm-package install doctor availability found only closed broad-audit/package-first lineage (pm-59gj, pm-kd9n, pm-etxf) and no open direct harness item. Desired outcome: script or npm task that discovers current external pm-cli/pm-package packages and runs isolated PM_PATH/PM_GLOBAL_PATH install, package doctor, and contracts availability probes with compact JSON output for agents."
type: Feature
status: closed
priority: 2
tags[5]: agent-ux,ecosystem,external-packages,package-first,test-harness
created_at: "2026-06-02T22:19:14.844Z"
updated_at: "2026-06-04T06:43:44.451Z"
author: codex-broad-audit-20260602
parent: pm-ugqx
resolution: "Shipped reusable external package smoke harness, public SDK in-memory activation test helper, docs, and Sentry gate handled-validation hygiene."
expected_result: Agents can verify external pm packages in isolated temp projects and package authors can test SDK extension registration through public helpers without private loader imports.
actual_result: "Added pnpm smoke:external-packages, activateExtensionForTest, package-author docs, release-gate allowlist coverage, and linked 11-command verification evidence with all commands passing."
comments[10]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-04T05:36:36.013Z",codex-sdk-cli-impl,"Start: continuing implementation-mode SDK/package-platform work. Duplicate check: pm context, pm search 'SDK package author customizable primitives context management', pm list-open, and pm list-in-progress found no active duplicate; reusing pm-vnjh under pm-ugqx. Sidecar agents launched for GitHub/security/release triage and SDK/package-author surface review."
  "2026-06-04T05:40:29.721Z",codex-sdk-cli-impl,"Evidence: focused external package smoke passed after harness argument-separator fix: pnpm smoke:external-packages -- --package pm-changelog returned ok=true, tested=1, failed=0, package doctor activation_failure_count=0, blocking_failure_count=0, and runtime contracts included changelog actions."
  "2026-06-04T05:42:06.731Z",codex-sdk-cli-impl,"Evidence: SDK sidecar under pm-ugqx added activateExtensionForTest to the public SDK testing surface, documented it in docs/SDK.md and docs/EXTENSIONS.md, and verified with sdk-index tests, pnpm build, and a manual temp npm consumer. Mainline focused verification also passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/sdk-index.spec.ts tests/unit/package-runtime-options.spec.ts (36 tests)."
  "2026-06-04T05:42:34.347Z",codex-sdk-cli-impl,"Evidence: linked tests passed with sandboxed PM_PATH/PM_GLOBAL_PATH: sdk/package focused tests, pnpm build, and pnpm smoke:external-packages -- --package pm-changelog all passed via pm test --run --progress. Additional gate passed: pnpm typecheck."
  "2026-06-04T05:56:05.172Z",codex-sdk-cli-impl,"Evidence: release-quality gates passed after fixes: node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage reached 100% statements/branches/functions/lines with 2216 tests; pnpm quality:static passed; pnpm quality:docs-skills passed; pnpm audit --audit-level moderate found no known vulnerabilities; pnpm security:scan found no credential-like secrets after pm history-redact removed a local absolute path from pm-ugqx history; pm validate --check-resolution --check-history-drift reported history_drift ok with existing resolution warnings; node scripts/release/sentry-telemetry-gate.mjs --json passed with critical=0 high=0 and PM-CLI-19 counted as expected handled CLI error; telemetry stack health showed all containers healthy enough, API ok, queue 0 ready/1 consumer, and 14539 events in last 24h."
  "2026-06-04T06:00:33.022Z",codex-sdk-cli-impl,"Evidence: package-owned changelog flow completed after close. pnpm changelog:pm installed pm-changelog 2026.6.4 and replaced CHANGELOG.md with item_count=955; pnpm changelog:pm:check then passed unchanged."
  "2026-06-04T06:11:24.691Z",codex-sdk-cli-impl,"Review response: addressed local PR feedback from Gemini/CodeRabbit/Codex. scripts/smoke-external-packages.mjs now resolves repoRoot from import.meta.url, reports spawnSync errors, creates PM_GLOBAL_PATH, wraps temp cleanup, and reports runtime actions from action_availability[].invocable. src/sdk/testing.ts now reads default-exported manifests and validates manifest.capabilities before spreading. Added SDK regression coverage for default-export manifests and malformed capabilities. Routed package-owned pm-changelog review findings upstream as unbraind/pm-changelog#26, #27, and #28 instead of patching generated managed extension code in pm-cli."
  "2026-06-04T06:18:41.703Z",codex-sdk-cli-impl,"Evidence: review-response linked rerun passed 12/12 commands after fixing bot findings. Coverage passed with 2218 tests and 100% statements/branches/functions/lines; subdirectory command cd scripts && node smoke-external-packages.mjs --discover-only --limit 1 passed; Sentry/telemetry, telemetry stack health, package smoke, build, typecheck, static/docs/security gates all passed."
  "2026-06-04T06:33:58.530Z",codex-sdk-package-smoke,"Evidence: addressed Gemini review feedback by letting activateExtensionForTest read direct metadata from in-memory extension modules and default exports. Added direct/default/capability-only regression coverage; focused SDK suite passed 29 tests, direct coverage passed 2221 tests at 100%, and pm-linked verification passed 12/12 commands including telemetry/Sentry, security scan, pm-changelog package smoke, build, docs/static, coverage, and typecheck."
  "2026-06-04T06:43:44.451Z",codex-sdk-package-smoke,"Evidence: addressed Gemini smoke-harness feedback by recording JSON parse failures as failed command entries, accepting comma/space-separated npm keyword strings during discovery, and filtering runtime action availability to invocable entries with string action names. Direct smoke checks passed: pnpm smoke:external-packages -- --package pm-changelog and cd scripts && node smoke-external-packages.mjs --discover-only --limit 1. Full pm-linked verification passed 12/12 commands with telemetry/Sentry, coverage, SDK/runtime, build, docs/static, security, package smoke, and typecheck green."
